.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, writing
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, badminton
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, western
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, trance
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, russian
House: futuristic, farmhouse
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, zinnia
1. the russian is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |
| Hobby         | dancing      | writing       |
| Sport           | basketball | badminton |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | horror        |
| Music-Genre   | folk         | trance        |
| Nationality   | pakistani    | russian       |
| House           | farmhouse        | futuristic          |
| Flower     | zinnia          | bellflower    |

