.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, reggae
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, june
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, teacher
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, egyptian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, ice-hockey
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, cain
1. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the dancer##3
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
3. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the argentine##3
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |
| Music-Genre      | dubstep | reggae  |
| Birthday          | june   | july   |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | puzzles   |
| Job           | dancer        | teacher   |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | argentine |
| Sport         | ice-hockey    | climbing  |
| Cigar     | bolivar       | cain      |

